channel.title: I need help with me webclient on my cache
channel.description:
i have 2 cache files one is mpr_file_store_32 and the other is file_store_32 how do i make them work with a webclient
can i just put them together? i just need help with this problem i am goin by rics tutorial
p.s. on his tutorial do i need to change my cache name to goodvbad_file_store_32?

item.title: I need help with me webclient on my cache
item.dc:creator: @D4rkscape D4rkscape
item.description:
@D4rkscape wrote:

yo dong, go to your client folder, look for sign, then go to signlink.java, then look for “File_store” no “”. then if it is that, then just do this “goodvbad_file_store_32” without the “”. then you will need to chat the file_store_32 in your cache file to goodvbad_file_store_32 as well. but now if you want other people to be able to download your cache when they run the webclient. do this… go back to singlink.java and change your “goodvbad_file_store_32” to “C:/goodvbad_file_store_32” without the “”. and then all you will need to do is put your cache which is goodvbad_file_store_32 in your c:/ drive and there u go! Hope this helped. =p
